---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page title="services -- alexander campos" description="AI automation, agentic SEO, cost optimization, and full online presence builds for small businesses.">
  <article>
    <h1>Services</h1>

    <p>
      I help businesses show up where it matters — to people and to the agents
      that increasingly find things for them. Most of this work pays for itself
      within a month.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <div class="services">
      <a data-cal-link="alexcampos/30min" class="service-card">
        <h2>Online Presence Build</h2>
        <p>Site, scheduling, forms, SEO, automations — one build, everything connected.</p>
      </a>
      <a data-cal-link="alexcampos/30min" class="service-card">
        <h2>Agentic SEO</h2>
        <p>Make your business findable by AI agents, not just search engines.</p>
      </a>
      <a data-cal-link="alexcampos/30min" class="service-card">
        <h2>AI Cost Optimization</h2>
        <p>Model routing that cuts API spend 40-60%. Audit included.</p>
      </a>
      <a data-cal-link="alexcampos/30min" class="service-card">
        <h2>Custom Automation</h2>
        <p>Describe the manual process. Get the pipeline.</p>
      </a>
      <a data-cal-link="alexcampos/30min" class="service-card">
        <h2>Claude & MCP Setup</h2>
        <p>Persistent memory, custom tools, team config. The setup that makes it useful.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <hr />

    <p class="pricing">
      Most engagements start with a 30-minute call. Pricing depends on scope.
    </p>

    <p class="contact-alt">
      Prefer email? <a href="mailto:adc.acampos@gmail.com">adc.acampos@gmail.com</a>
    </p>
  </article>

  <script is:inline src="/islands/cal-embed.js"></script>

  <script is:inline>
    console.log(
      '%c the infrastructure is the product. ',
      'color: #E8DCC8; font-family: monospace; font-size: 11px;'
    );
  </script>
</Page>

<style>
  .services {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .service-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--white-08);
    padding: 1rem 1.15rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold-accent);
  }

  .service-card h2 {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
    color: var(--glow);
  }

  .service-card p {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--white-45);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .services {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .pricing {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--white-45);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-alt {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--white-30);
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
